{"tid":2302423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國總統川普重申2020大選「我贏了！」","createTime":"2020-11-27T06:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-27T08:37:41.000Z","uid":337052,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c3aa697f4ff296fa99db47a39a8561cf00a778d8","tid":2302423,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:05:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">川普推特又嗆假新聞 重申2020大選「我贏了！」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2020/11/27 13:25<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">美國總統川普今天舉行感恩節記者會，事後在推特批評「假新聞媒體」不會報導他真正想傳遞的訊息，川普重申2020年美國總統大選是被操控的，「我贏了！」</span><br />\n<br />\n川普在推特上還砲轟了推特，稱推特只會發布錯誤的趨勢，與世界上真正的趨勢不同，而是些負面的東西，推特會落到跟《福斯新聞》收視率下降一樣的下場。川普強調，為了國家安全，應該廢除美國《通訊規範法》第230條。<br />\n<br />\n該法條容許社交平台不用承擔使用者張貼內容的責任，並賦予其限制平台上內容的權力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1332169753004224515?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1332169753004224515%3Fs%3D20&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=a8c0bf13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1332169753004224515%3Fs%3D20&h=680a6a5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1332169753004224515?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3364097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3364097&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=568e53c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3364097&h=7235152b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3364097</a>"},{"pid":"337ecee2bb35b3791c6a0c3df46f836b452078c2","tid":2302423,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:07:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">六州的法律訴訟成為翻盤重點</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n賓夕法尼亞州，喬治亞州，密歇根州，威斯康星州，亞利桑那州和內華達州<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theepochtimes.com/election-findings-could-easily-overturn-3-states-data-analyst-concludes_3595153.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theepochtimes.com%2Felection-findings-could-easily-overturn-3-states-data-analyst-concludes_3595153.html&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=82f0c09d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theepochtimes.com/election-findings-could-easily-overturn-3-states-data-analyst-concludes_3595153.html</a>"},{"pid":"16c7fedc97a8d7247734e37da3027e77c8e839ad","tid":2302423,"uid":318316,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"唔敢咁大期望, <br />\n驚希望越大失望越大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106ba4c9eea8aa346870245080a649805ffa1c0b","tid":2302423,"uid":1886,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:10:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"violet\">老鳳懷疑張奕鈞先生(SimonTW #337052)為在台共諜</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2299129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2299129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">SimonTW條台灣白卡佬<br />\n恭喜周庭同gphone要坐監<br />\n屈鳩周庭支持抖音<br />\n叫香港人同佢地割蓆<br />\n大家要一齊屌到佢仆街</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WXm7PfN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWXm7PfN.png&h=24baa447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恭喜周庭和黃之峰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2296813\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2296813</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">此人往績</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n小心此人，一邊聲稱支持港人，一邊要求與同路人割蓆。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eTbf8hj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeTbf8hj.png&h=48d2f38a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/226kMUH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F226kMUH.png&h=24a6b752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2vGTavG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2vGTavG.png&h=6ad271ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HzzViub.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzzViub.png&h=81163fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dgZEPXY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdgZEPXY.jpg&h=f8ebe2e7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開心啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aAGDAsV\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aAGDAsV</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aAGDAvV\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aAGDAvV</a><br />\n<br />\n惟仍堅拒收回相關言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aBdeHOV\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aBdeHOV</a><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1JTfAKz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1JTfAKz.png&h=0e1baf9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0FSoKD9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0FSoKD9.png&h=69f2ba0c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOne More Thing<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xvxDzJh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxvxDzJh.png&h=060a084d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSimonTW 台灣護照<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">無碼高清</span></span></strong>版<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/azoGvGV\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/azoGvGV</a><br />\n#26 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8f1c39d498baae3351db1383dddb4ee988a4ccab","tid":2302423,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:10:15.000Z","msg":"任期最後兩個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3022ecd3b3012630fef495c57065704754393248","tid":2302423,"uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:11:04.000Z","msg":"打小陣飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9142086246950c7ec9641dd55304c68c7924fa","tid":2302423,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:11:36.000Z","msg":"會員編號：#337052<br />\r會員註冊日期：2019/11/1<br />\r入 LIST 原因：恭喜周庭和黃之鋒要入獄，早前又抹黑蘋果日報，指收費是吃人血饅頭，認為自由應是無價。<br />\r <br />\r<a href=\"https://bit.ly/lihkg_on9_list\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Flihkg_on9_list&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=884c899c\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/lihkg_on9_list</a><br />\r <br />\r<blockquote><img src=\"https://filedn.com/lFVbsBoM5LqyM5pzAQLoN44/IMG/LIHKG_on9/337052/337052.1_.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.com%2FlFVbsBoM5LqyM5pzAQLoN44%2FIMG%2FLIHKG_on9%2F337052%2F337052.1_.png&h=2f386de0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r<img src=\"https://filedn.com/lFVbsBoM5LqyM5pzAQLoN44/IMG/LIHKG_on9/337052/337052.2_.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.com%2FlFVbsBoM5LqyM5pzAQLoN44%2FIMG%2FLIHKG_on9%2F337052%2F337052.2_.png&h=16b55125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r<img src=\"https://filedn.com/lFVbsBoM5LqyM5pzAQLoN44/IMG/LIHKG_on9/337052/337052.3_.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.com%2FlFVbsBoM5LqyM5pzAQLoN44%2FIMG%2FLIHKG_on9%2F337052%2F337052.3_.png&h=01ce4566&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\r <br />\r<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r <br />\r<em><span class=\"small\">上述資料更新日期：2020/11/24<br />\rP.S. 呢個唔係五毛 LIST，係戇鳩 LIST，可以畀大家認識到比較特別嘅會員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span></em>"},{"pid":"612111931018f717d252cd3137b9b29b8927c3b8","tid":2302423,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:12:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">中國介入大選？ 美媒爆：Dominion背後有解放軍背景</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2020/11/27 11:32<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">美國媒體爆料，美國大選多州使用的Dominion投票系統（Dominion Voting Systems）與中共軍方有關聯，該系統的關鍵技術人員安迪‧黃（Andy Huang）曾在有解放軍背景的企業任職過。</span><br />\n<br />\n美國右派媒體《國家脈動》（National Pulse）報導，黃在Dominion擔任關鍵技術職務，為現任地區投票系統訊息技術核心基礎架構的經理，但在1998年至2002年期間，他任職於中國電信（China Telecom），負責「廈門IDC項目」、「廈門市區寬頻網路」和「OA Intranet基礎設施改造項目」等項目。<br />\n<br />\n報導提到，儘管外界對這些項目的具體性質尚未完全清楚，但中國電信是由中共政府全資經營，並被美國國防部認定為與解放軍合作超過20年。川普政府已將中國電信列為「中共軍工企業」黑名單，限制美國人對其進行投資。<br />\n<br />\n《國家脈動》報導，美國情報官員已經證實，北京更願意讓拜登擔任總統，因此關於黃的這個新發現，增加Dominion公司與中共有關聯的猜測。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3363960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3363960&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=77548b48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3363960&h=8f1ad505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3363960</a>"},{"pid":"8d0e0b96c1e77d4f71a782694c6d508520a9fa8d","tid":2302423,"uid":371558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:12:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe8e73d18f4ab8c2c51f70fbdbcdfda26711a90d","tid":2302423,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f1c39d498baae3351db1383dddb4ee988a4ccab","tid":2302423,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:10:15.000Z","msg":"任期最後兩個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:13:40.000Z","msg":"選舉人投票是關鍵"},{"pid":"ce7239adf375d3656feba0ca5d080fcedc3d9af9","tid":2302423,"uid":132729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:15:15.000Z","msg":"咁嬴到未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09155e473a529116261d595195be28b85425696b","tid":2302423,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce7239adf375d3656feba0ca5d080fcedc3d9af9","tid":2302423,"uid":132729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:15:15.000Z","msg":"咁嬴到未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"還沒<br />\n先利用法律戰拖延選舉人投票"},{"pid":"a3edd3d22e87afec4888197d9a853a5d49bb175d","tid":2302423,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:10:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">川普律師朱利安尼：選舉舞弊證據「如山高」 現在只是冰山一角</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2020/11/27 14:06<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">川普私人律師朱利安尼（Rudy Giuliani）25日表示，川普的法律團隊握有「如山高的」選舉舞弊證據，現在看到的只不過是冰山一角。</span><br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓觀察家報》（Washington Examiner）報導，川普陣營25日在賓州蓋茨堡（Gettysburg）舉行選舉舞弊聽證會，朱利安尼指出，這次聽證會是川普團隊首次能夠提供證據的真正機會，主流媒體和法官都在掩蓋這樣的消息，「他們不希望美國人民聽到詐欺的證據......我們有如山高的證據，我們只拿出少量做為代表。」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">朱利安尼強調，如果賓州的計票結果是假的，而州選務官員認證了該結果，這些人就犯下偽證罪。</span><br />\n<br />\n報導提到，川普團隊的時間已不多，因為各州的選舉人團將在12月14日開會投票，就目前情況而言，拜登擁有306張選舉人票，而川普則有232張票。一個州的翻盤還不足以讓川普獲勝，川普法律團隊和盟友也將目光投向其他關鍵州，包括喬治亞州和內華達州。<br />\n<br />\n11月30日，亞利桑那州議會將召開選舉調查聽證會；12月份，密西根州州議會也將召開類似聽證會；喬治亞州和內華達州的法官則將在12月3日舉行聽證會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3364099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3364099&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=625bd032\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3364099&h=92ea6218\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3364099</a>"},{"pid":"a7d595305b7948b79491c91321751df2f7fc5132","tid":2302423,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:12:06.000Z","msg":"大妓院<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5771e09655da727ff3e76eaba45d6cabcb2a8634","tid":2302423,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:12:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>SimonTW 對自己早前抹黑周庭和黃之鋒一事之回應</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0JFZdR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0JFZdR.png&h=d0e14ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4afbd23b5a1c08d681e8562113a992991fd859","tid":2302423,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T07:13:36.000Z","msg":"Think big<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7e790703fcf6e7efcda218f7247a606ebc1476","tid":2302423,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T08:31:24.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普今天舉行感恩節記者會，事後在推特批評「假新聞媒體」不會報導他真正想傳遞的訊息，川普重申2020年美國總統大選是被操控的，「我贏了！」"},{"pid":"90fa7ce8bec1edfe89deeffef362588da54195fe","tid":2302423,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16c7fedc97a8d